<a href="/articles/24773.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/24773/indexMediumPc2/24773.jpg?1459402678" alt="《蜜桃女孩》改编成真人电影，傻黑甜少女恋爱了">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/3/medium/3.png?1411569578" alt="娱乐">
			<span>娱乐</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">《蜜桃女孩》改编成真人电影，傻黑甜少女恋爱了</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-31 14:06:40 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
